This paper is primarily focused on computer vision and deep learning techniques for visual place recognition. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of multi-scale feature encoding and classification techniques, which are relevant to the Robotics (cs.RO) and Machine Learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE) sub-categories.
